This E!Cockput Archive contains a demo of publishing and subscribing via MQTT. It contains all necessary libraries as well.
The subscription program has not been added to the Task Configuration in this example - but can simply be added if wanted.

https://www.dropbox.com/s/iknknxwifwib53x/FW17%20-%20MQTT%20-%20New%20PubSub%20Example.eca?dl=0
